blue(x) = blue_a * exp(- (x - blue_u) ** 2 / (2 * blue_o ** 2)) / (blue_o * sqrt(2 * pi)) + blue_a1 * exp(- (x - blue_u1) ** 2 / (2 * blue_o1 ** 2)) / (blue_o1 * sqrt(2 * pi)) + blue_a2 * exp(- (x - blue_u2) ** 2 / (2 * blue_o2 ** 2)) / (blue_o2 * sqrt(2 * pi))

